item.title: Aircraft Model Collection in 2017
item.description: Info: This post covers all my aircraft models which collected in 2017. ID photo and basic model information: Order from newest to oldest [JC Wings] Hainan Airlines B787-9, B-7302 “Kung Fu Panda (yellow)” Special Colour. Arrived at 2017-12-05. [Phoenix] Qantas A380-800, VH-OQK. Arrived at 2017-10-31. [Phoenix] Singapore Airlines A380-800, 9V-SKT. Arrived at 2017-10-31. [Phoenix] All Nippon Airways B777-200ER, JA745A. Arrived at 2017-10-31.

item.title: Aircraft Model Collection in 2014
item.description: Info: This post covers all my aircraft models which collected in 2014. Time flies very fasts…There was a large number models back to 2014. However, only 4 girls remained here today. ID photo and basic model information: Order from newest to oldest [Phoenix] China Airlines A330-300 B-18358 “Masalu Taiwan!” Special Colour. Arrived at 2014-09-08.
